{"tid":1715481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立會外垃圾桶爆炸案　佔中輔警楊逸朗囚兩年","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:03:57.000Z","uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"760460c9998a665fcec010831e830ea28f8dfe16","tid":1715481,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FRgyilX2n7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFRgyilX2n7U&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=05ddcb8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FRgyilX2n7U</a><br />\n警方繼續調查前日立會大樓外示威區發生的垃圾桶爆炸案，並鎖定兩名涉案在逃口罩男。<br />\n<br />\n立會原定周三恢復二讀備受爭議的《2014年版權（修訂）條例草案》，惟流會後，晚上立會綜合大樓示威區垃圾桶發生爆炸案。警方港島重案組總督察陳仲權表示，前晚8時30分接獲立法會秘書處報案．指立會綜合大樓示威區垃圾桶發生爆炸，經調查後發現，當時有兩名男子走近垃圾桶，燃點物體並扔入垃圾桶，隨即冒出火舌及爆炸；兩人其後向添馬公園逃去。陳稱相信爆炸裝置是改裝的氣體罐。<br />\n<br />\n哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！炸垃圾筒好暴力好唔理性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好學呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}